The paper focuses on visual question answering, which involves computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper proposes a new model for visual attention, which involves machine learning and optimization techniques, making it relevant to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
